sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as K8s API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as modelmesh-controller<br/>ServiceAccount Auth
    participant etcd as etcd Cluster<br/>2379/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Gateway as Istio Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant RESTProxy as REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh<br/>8085/TCP gRPC mTLS
    participant RuntimeAdapter as Runtime Adapter<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant ModelRuntime as Model Runtime<br/>8001/TCP gRPC
    participant StorageHelper as Storage Helper<br/>8086/TCP gRPC
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: Model Deployment

    User->>K8sAPI: POST Predictor CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch notification<br/>ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment<br/>ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>etcd: Register model metadata<br/>Client cert auth
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Deployment created
    Controller->>StorageHelper: Request model pull<br/>8086/TCP gRPC
    StorageHelper->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>AWS IAM/Access Key
    S3-->>StorageHelper: Model files
    StorageHelper-->>ModelMesh: Model loaded notification
    ModelMesh->>RuntimeAdapter: Load model<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    RuntimeAdapter->>ModelRuntime: Initialize model<br/>8001/TCP gRPC
    ModelRuntime-->>RuntimeAdapter: Ready
    RuntimeAdapter-->>ModelMesh: Ready
    ModelMesh->>etcd: Update model status
    Controller-->>User: Predictor ready

    Note over User,S3: Flow 2: Inference Request (REST)

    User->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/model:infer<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
    Gateway->>RESTProxy: Forward<br/>8008/TCP HTTP
    RESTProxy->>ModelMesh: gRPC predict<br/>8085/TCP mTLS (optional)
    ModelMesh->>RuntimeAdapter: Route to runtime<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    RuntimeAdapter->>ModelRuntime: Inference<br/>8001/TCP gRPC
    ModelRuntime-->>RuntimeAdapter: Prediction result
    RuntimeAdapter-->>ModelMesh: Result
    ModelMesh-->>RESTProxy: gRPC response
    RESTProxy-->>Gateway: HTTP response
    Gateway-->>User: JSON result

    Note over User,S3: Flow 3: Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Bearer Token
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics
